lected_at": "2026-06-04T11:27:33.565927+00:00", "source": "google_maps_scrape"}, {"review_id": "ba5d5fd1706a09a608f3d4c923920147", "station_name": "IndianOil Petrol Pump (Goregaon)", "station_address": "Dindoshi, Goregaon East, Mumbai, Maharashtra 400063", "station_rating": 3.8, "station_reviews": 1877.0, "brand": "IndianOil", "category": "Petrol Pump", "zone": "North Suburbs", "lat": 19.1754031, "lng": 72.8661922, "author_name": "Saurabh Shetty", "rating": 4.0, "text": "The Indian Oil Petrol Pump is a reliable spot for fueling up, offering good service and quality fuel. The facilities are well-maintained, and the staff are efficient and courteous, ensuring a smooth experience for customers.\n\nHowever, it tends to get quite crowded, especially with bikes, which can lead to some delays. Despite the congestion, the service remains quick and professional. If you can visit during off-peak hours, your experience will likely be even better. Overall, it’s a nice and dependable petrol pump, albeit a bit busy at times.", "date_relative": "a year ago", "date_iso": "2026-06-04T11:27:33.565927+00:00", "collected_at": "2026-06-04T11:27:33.565927+00:00", "source": "google_maps_scrape"}, {"review_id": "ba5d5fd1706a09a608f3d4c923920147", "station_name": "IndianOil Petrol Pump (Goregaon)", "station_address": "Dindoshi, Goregaon East, Mumbai, Maharashtra 400063", "station_rating": 3.8, "station_reviews": 1877.0, "brand": "IndianOil", "category": "Petrol Pump", "zone": "North Suburbs", "lat": 19.1754031, "lng": 72.8661922, "author_name": "Saurabh Shetty", "rating": 4.0, "text": "The Indian Oil Petrol Pump is a reliable spot for fueling up, offering good service and quality fuel. The facilities are well-maintained, and the staff are efficient and courteous, ensuring a smooth experience for customers.\n\nHowever, it tends to get quite crowded, especially with bikes, which can lead to some delays. Despite the congestion, the service remains quick and professional. If you can visit durin